<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>과사람 자사관 프로젝트 | 2026 1학기 중간고사 대비</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;600;700;900&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --navy: #1B2A4A;
  --navy-light: #2C3E6B;
  --orange: #E8731A;
  --orange-light: #F5A623;
  --orange-glow: rgba(232, 115, 26, 0.15);
  --white: #FFFFFF;
  --gray-50: #F8F9FC;
  --gray-100: #EEF1F6;
  --gray-200: #D8DDE8;
  --gray-400: #8E99B0;
  --gray-600: #5A6477;
  --gray-800: #2D3442;
  --text: #1a1a2e;
  --radius: 16px;
  --radius-sm: 10px;
  --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(27,42,74,0.06);
  --shadow-md: 0 8px 32px rgba(27,42,74,0.10);
  --shadow-lg: 0 16px 48px rgba(27,42,74,0.14);
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

body {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  background: var(--gray-50);
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.7;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

/* ── Hero ── */
.hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-light) 60%, #3a5298 100%);
  color: var(--white);
  padding: 56px 24px 48px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -40%;
  right: -20%;
  width: 500px;
  height: 500px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,115,26,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
  border-radius: 50%;
}
.hero-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  padding: 6px 20px;
  border-radius: 100px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  animation: fadeDown 0.6s ease-out;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 38px);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1.3;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  animation: fadeDown 0.6s ease-out 0.1s both;
}
.hero h1 em {
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--orange-light);
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 300;
  opacity: 0.8;
  max-width: 420px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  animation: fadeDown 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both;
}

/* ── Container ── */
.container {
  max-width: 680px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 20px;
}

/* ── Section ── */
.section {
  margin-top: 36px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease-out both;
}
.section:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
.section:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
.section:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
.section:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }

.section-label {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--orange);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.section-label::before {
  content: '';
  width: 18px;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--orange);
  border-radius: 2px;
}

.section-title {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--navy);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

/* ── Cards ── */
.card {
  background: var(--white);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 28px 24px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
  transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
}
.card:hover {
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* ── Two-Track ── */
.track-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 14px;
}
@media (max-width: 560px) {
  .track-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
.track-card {
  background: var(--white);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 24px 20px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: box-shadow 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
}
.track-card:hover {
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}
.track-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 4px;
}
.track-card.diagnosis::before { background: var(--navy); }
.track-card.advanced::before { background: var(--orange); }

.track-num {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.track-card.diagnosis .track-num { color: var(--navy-light); }
.track-card.advanced .track-num { color: var(--orange); }

.track-title {
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--navy);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.track-en {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.track-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gray-600);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.track-items {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
}
.track-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--gray-800);
  padding: 10px 14px;
  background: var(--gray-50);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
}
.track-item .icon {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 14px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.track-card.diagnosis .icon { background: rgba(27,42,74,0.08); }
.track-card.advanced .icon { background: var(--orange-glow); }

/* ── Timeline ── */
.timeline {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 36px;
}
.timeline::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 13px;
  top: 8px;
  bottom: 8px;
  width: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--navy), var(--orange));
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.tl-item {
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.tl-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.tl-dot {
  position: absolute;
  left: -30px;
  top: 6px;
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--navy);
  border: 3px solid var(--gray-50);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--navy);
}
.tl-item.highlight .tl-dot {
  background: var(--orange);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--orange);
}

.tl-date {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--navy);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.tl-item.highlight .tl-date { color: var(--orange); }

.tl-title {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gray-800);
  margin-bottom: 3px;
}
.tl-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gray-600);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.tl-time-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 100px;
  background: var(--gray-100);
  color: var(--gray-600);
  margin-top: 6px;
}

/* ── Schedule Table ── */
.schedule-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: separate;
  border-spacing: 0 6px;
}
.schedule-table th {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  text-align: left;
  padding: 0 12px 8px;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.schedule-table td {
  padding: 14px 12px;
  font-size: 13px;
  background: var(--white);
}
.schedule-table tr td:first-child {
  border-radius: 10px 0 0 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--navy);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.schedule-table tr td:last-child {
  border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
}
.schedule-table .tool-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  margin-right: 6px;
}
.badge-orange { background: var(--orange-glow); color: var(--orange); }
.badge-navy { background: rgba(27,42,74,0.08); color: var(--navy); }

/* ── Steps ── */
.steps-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 48px;
}
.step-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 16px;
  position: relative;
  padding: 12px 0;
}
.step-num {
  position: absolute;
  left: -48px;
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--white);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.step-num.navy { background: var(--navy); }
.step-num.orange { background: var(--orange); }

.step-content {
  flex: 1;
}
.step-title {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gray-800);
  margin-bottom: 2px;
}
.step-desc {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
}
.step-connector {
  position: absolute;
  left: -32px;
  top: 44px;
  width: 2px;
  height: calc(100% - 32px);
  background: var(--gray-200);
}
.step-row:last-child .step-connector { display: none; }

/* ── Promise circle ── */
.promise-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
  text-align: center;
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .promise-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
.promise-item {
  background: var(--white);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 24px 16px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
  transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
}
.promise-item:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}
.promise-icon {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 22px;
  margin: 0 auto 12px;
}
.promise-icon.pi-1 { background: rgba(27,42,74,0.08); }
.promise-icon.pi-2 { background: var(--orange-glow); }
.promise-icon.pi-3 { background: rgba(58,82,152,0.1); }

.promise-num {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--orange);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.promise-title {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--navy);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.promise-desc {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--gray-600);
  line-height: 1.5;
}

/* ── CTA Footer ── */
.cta-section {
  margin-top: 40px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  text-align: center;
}
.cta-box {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-light) 100%);
  color: var(--white);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 36px 24px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.cta-box::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -30px;
  right: -30px;
  width: 120px;
  height: 120px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,115,26,0.2), transparent);
  border-radius: 50%;
}
.cta-quote {
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.cta-quote em {
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--orange-light);
}
.cta-sub {
  font-size: 13px;
  opacity: 0.7;
  font-weight: 300;
}

/* ── Animations ── */
@keyframes fadeDown {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-16px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* ── Global touch ── */
::selection {
  background: var(--orange);
  color: white;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Hero -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">자사관 프로젝트</div>
  <h1>2026년 1학기<br><em>중간고사 대비</em> 상세 계획</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">완벽한 내신 대비를 위한 맞춤형 학습 및 특화 프로그램</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <!-- Two-Track -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">SYSTEM</div>
    <div class="section-title">투트랙(Two-Track) 시스템</div>
    <div class="track-grid">
      <div class="track-card diagnosis">
        <div class="track-num">TRACK 01</div>
        <div class="track-title">개별 맞춤 학습</div>
        <div class="track-en">Diagnosis & Care</div>
        <div class="track-desc">학생별 수준과 상황에 맞춘<br>데이터 기반 밀착 관리</div>
        <div class="track-items">
          <div class="track-item"><span class="icon">📋</span> 미리보는 중간고사 (중2, 3)</div>
          <div class="track-item"><span class="icon">🔍</span> 약점 보완 개별 클리닉</div>
          <div class="track-item"><span class="icon">⚡</span> 시험 직전 보강</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="track-card advanced">
        <div class="track-num">TRACK 02</div>
        <div class="track-title">내신 특화 수업</div>
        <div class="track-en">Advanced Skill Building</div>
        <div class="track-desc">최상위권 고득점을 위한<br>핵심 수학적 역량 강화</div>
        <div class="track-items">
          <div class="track-item"><span class="icon">✍️</span> 서술형 완벽 대비 집중 수업</div>
          <div class="track-item"><span class="icon">📊</span> 내신 대비 기출 분석 특화 수업</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 1단계: 미리보는 중간고사 -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">STEP 1</div>
    <div class="section-title">미리보는 중간고사</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:20px;">
        <span style="font-size:12px; font-weight:600; background:var(--gray-100); padding:5px 14px; border-radius:100px; color:var(--gray-600);">대상: 중학교 2, 3학년</span>
        <span style="font-size:12px; font-weight:600; background:var(--orange-glow); padding:5px 14px; border-radius:100px; color:var(--orange);">시행일: 3월 28일</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; margin-bottom:20px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:var(--gray-600); line-height:1.7;">
          <strong style="color:var(--gray-800);">🏫 오프라인 등원</strong><br>
          오전 10:00~13:00 또는<br>오후 14:00~17:00 중 선택
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:var(--gray-600); line-height:1.7;">
          <strong style="color:var(--gray-800);">💻 온라인 진행</strong><br>
          정해진 시간 엄수
        </div>
      </div>
      <table class="schedule-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>시간</th><th>내용</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>10:00~10:40</td>
            <td><span class="tool-badge badge-orange">오르조 앱</span>동래구 지역 2025년 기출 1</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>10:50~11:30</td>
            <td><span class="tool-badge badge-orange">오르조 앱</span>동래구 지역 2025년 기출 2</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>11:40~12:20</td>
            <td><span class="tool-badge badge-navy">클래스인</span>서술형 문제 풀이</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>12:30~13:00</td>
            <td><span class="tool-badge badge-navy">분석</span>틀린 문제 완벽 분석 · 1:1 피드백</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 2단계: 개별 클리닉 -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">STEP 2</div>
    <div class="section-title">개별 클리닉 및 직전 보강</div>
    <div class="card">
      <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--gray-600); margin-bottom:20px; padding:12px 16px; background:var(--gray-50); border-radius:var(--radius-sm); border-left:3px solid var(--orange);">
        '미리보는 중간고사' 성적 데이터 분석 결과에 따라<br>개별 등원 대상자 선정 (약점 집중 케어)
      </p>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="tl-item">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-date">4월 4일 (토)</div>
          <div class="tl-title">1차 개별 클리닉</div>
          <div class="tl-desc">미리보는 중간고사 결과에 따라 뚜렷한 약점 단원이 있거나 집중 개별 케어가 필요한 학생 대상</div>
          <span class="tl-time-badge">10:00 ~ 13:00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-item">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-date">4월 11일 (토)</div>
          <div class="tl-title">2차 개별 클리닉</div>
          <div class="tl-desc">1차 클리닉 이후에도 보완이 필요하거나 부모님·학생 요청이 있는 경우 추가 진행</div>
          <span class="tl-time-badge">10:00 ~ 13:00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-item highlight">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-date">D-1 (시험 전날)</div>
          <div class="tl-title">최종 직전 보강</div>
          <div class="tl-desc">시험 전날 마지막 점검 및 핵심 정리</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 특화 수업 1: 서술형 -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">SPECIAL 1</div>
    <div class="section-title">서술형 대비 특화 수업</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:24px;">
        <span style="font-size:12px; font-weight:600; background:var(--gray-100); padding:5px 14px; border-radius:100px; color:var(--gray-600);">수업 시간: 20:30 ~ 22:00</span>
        <span style="font-size:12px; font-weight:600; background:rgba(27,42,74,0.08); padding:5px 14px; border-radius:100px; color:var(--navy);">플랫폼: 클래스인 (100% 복습 가능)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-container">
        <div class="step-row">
          <div class="step-num navy">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">핵심 조건과 단서 명시</div>
            <div class="step-desc">문제의 의도 파악</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-connector"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row">
          <div class="step-num navy">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">순서도 작성</div>
            <div class="step-desc">문제 해결을 위한 논리적 플로우 기획</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-connector"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row">
          <div class="step-num navy">3</div>
